reviewText:
I know that some will disagree with me with my opinion on the video.
They will say that the Cannabis Cup has become over-commercialized and has been over-run by tourists from the U.S.
But duh -- that was what the movie was trying to show.
Don't buy this video if you are looking for bud shots or anything like that.
This is just a video that shows the events things that go on at the yearly Cannabis Cup and what to expect if you go there.
It is more like a - if you go (video), this is what to expect.
I felt like this video was interesting, especially since I have never gone before.
